    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts precisely, making it a dependable choice for any driver. While the exterior is generally clean, you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches consistent with normal use. The interior is in great shape with no tears in the upholstery, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. All electronics and climate control systems are fully functional, and the tires have plenty of tread remaining. This is a solid, honest car that is ready for its next owner.",
