      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is ideal for a buyer looking for a project or a source for parts. While the car is currently tow-away or requires immediate mechanical attention, the engine struggles with significant oil leaks and a very rough idle. The exterior shows noticeable rust and paint fade, and the interior has seen heavy wear over the years. This is a fix-it-up special for someone with the right tools and time.",
