      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks and feels great on the road? I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in solid shape, well-loved, and ready for its next adventure with you. It runs super smooth and has plenty of life left in it. I\u2019ve priced it for a quick sale because I\u2019m looking for a smooth, easy hand-off to someone who will appreciate it. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 28900.0,
