    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. Proactive maintenance includes a reinforced rear subframe and a cooling system overhaul. While the exterior shows minor signs of road use, the mechanical vitals\u2014including compression across all cylinders and suspension geometry\u2014remain sharp. A visceral, analog performer for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
