    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained sedan that perfectly captures the balance between daily utility and refined comfort. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, showing only the lightest signs of road use, such as minor stone chips on the front bumper that are typical for its age. All body panels are straight, and the alloy wheels are free of major curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a non-smoker environment where the leather seating has been treated regularly to prevent cracking, resulting in a supple feel and excellent support. Every electronic feature, from the heated seats to the premium navigation system, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health; it has received synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles, and the most recent service included a comprehensive multi-point inspection, new brake pads, and a fresh set of all-season tires. The engine runs quietly, and the transmission provides seamless shifts under both city and highway conditions. This vehicle comes with a complete service history and is ready to be driven home today.",
